Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like the village where\NI lived with Pa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:14.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who suggested coming here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doubt if we'll find a shard\nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:23.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome... are you picking up\nany vibes from a Jewel Shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, let's split up and look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Catch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going off alone\nto pick up some woman, Monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh! I sense a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you be so callous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We haven't even started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If there's a demon around,\NI'll smell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He plans to goof off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahh... such nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Shippo's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? He probably went off to play.\NHe's just a kid, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boy, the pains I go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been in a lot of battles lately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They deserve to be alone\nfor a change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:40.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Liar! You stole the dried\npersimmon from my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did not! Did you see me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:04:00.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you! When my brother\ncomes home, you'll all get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:04.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! Your brother died long ago\nin the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My pa was with him when\nhe died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My brother's NOT dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You lying thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghhh! A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That'll show 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:45.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Thank you, raccoon-dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For saving me... want half?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The dried persimmon I stole.\NIt's yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}S- She was the culprit, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're strong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Satsuki.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I'm Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... cool name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My pa named me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah? So your pa is a\nraccoon-dog demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, a fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki, don't you have parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They died right after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I have a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:39.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gonna prove himself in battle\nand become a samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then he's coming for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Were those kids lying then?\NDidn't your brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if he dies, he'll come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll show only you.\NIt's my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anything I wish on it\nwill come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty? It's a piece\nof something called...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Jewel of Four Souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}T- The Jewel of Four Souls?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother, what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a shard from the Jewel of Four Souls\nwhich grants any wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll become a samurai\nwithout fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brother wouldn't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is my home possessed\nby some demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, we must exorcise it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:59.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my duty as a monk.\NI expect no payment, Headman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall provide meals and a place to sleep\nfor you all this night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Miroku... lying through\nhis teeth again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,E-Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... there {\i1}was{\i0} a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you weren't lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:44.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:46.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, how did you find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I figured Miroku would be\nperforming an exorcism at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the finest-looking house in\nthe village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:00.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I found it...\nthe Sacred Jewel Shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, will you show me\nyour shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't take it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will!\NIf it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\nljust want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! If it's real, we'll have\nto take it from her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Satsuki's wish won't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:41.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, stupid me! What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! Stupid me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's enough.\NI'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NBe careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it okay to let her go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:01.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki! Have you changed\nyour mind about living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Brother will come home\nsome day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome... that shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, that was\na stone flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stone flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, a quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can dig it up in\nthe mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not a Sacred Jewel Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki is a pitiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her brother {\i1}really{\i0} is dead,\nbut she won't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please bring Brother\nback home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've told her to come live with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but she refuses to move from that hut\nshe shared with her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was chased out of the\nheadman's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I can use that little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll teach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:18.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel has the power to\ncreate incarnations of Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So if a wish is made on\na real Sacred Jewel Shard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will Satsuki's brother be resurrected\nand return home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geometry scares me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:07.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:11.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Inuyasha!\NI thought you were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let me go!\NIt's to help someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, you know just\nhow frightening the Sacred Jewel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not something you give\nto humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, why are you taking pity\non that little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's smitten with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was quite cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what if I'm in love with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:44.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at you! Flitting back\nand forth between Kikyo and Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,B-Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've waited a long time.\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew... I knew that you would\ncome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say good-bye at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:46.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Satsuki will keep\nwishing on that fake shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:51.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I can't tell her the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:54.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My wish came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brother is home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, where's Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't he with that girl, Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was very worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki's brother is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but she has faith in that shard\nand keeps waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Butting in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Kagome.\NI'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? He's hurt, but Brother's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:43.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki... It's all thanks to you\nand the Sacred Jewel Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A demon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:14:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brother, hurry and get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... I made you suffer\na long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make up for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Satsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:11.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you're with the group staying\nat the headman's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you bring it to me...\nthe real Sacred Jewel Shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let Satsuki go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have the Sacred Jewel Shard\nright here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you tell... this is junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's totally useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki cherished that shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:54.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now kid... go and get me\nthe real Sacred Jewel Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or else... I'll break Satsuki's neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your brother, who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Show your true self, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You coulda let her believe\NI was her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!\NI'll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dang! He figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki, get away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? No way!\NI can't leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This takes only one passenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this Satsuki's hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:32.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See this? It's a crawling,\nbig-bellied demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like it got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miroku!\NWe've gotta go after Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay alive, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Shippo's fox magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good job, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo's being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:03.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Satsuki, I hope you got away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may've let the girl go,\nbut it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use you as a hostage\nto get a Sacred Jewel Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you come after\nme from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dashed Satsuki's hopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interesting... Want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get a taste of my stomach acid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:49.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Multiply!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!\NBombs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:55.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...\NI've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is my powertoo weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't I fight like the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Playtime's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Turned yourself into\nsomething weird again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Got a gripe with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can test the Backlash Wave\nwhich I've just mastered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Locate the demonic aura,\ntwist it around the Wind Scar...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then reverse the flow-\nmy new ultimate technique!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:13.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Backlash Wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:14.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! This opponent's demonic energy\nis too weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't use the Backlash Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you mumbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just too weak, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:39.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? This is the demon I exorcised\nfrom the headman's house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Shippo...\nyou did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, you beat the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It wasn't me. Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:07.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I arrived, the demon\nwas already beaten to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:15.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This demon figured he didn't have\na chance with us, so he used Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone who tries to use\nthe Sacred Jewel encounters unhappiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:25.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I forgot that... and Satsuki suffered\nfor it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:47.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've decided... to go live with\nthe headman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew all along\nthat my brother was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care, Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:08.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shippo!\NI'm glad I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Satsuki, find happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have a Ma or Pa either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:22.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm not alone. That's why\NI can go on living.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was Shippo really in love\nwith that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Acting like a grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's little, but he's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:57.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Shippo! If you lag behind\nwe'll leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:53.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the men in a village are bewitched\nby a demon princess and won't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku sets out alone\nto rescue them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:59.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but his one weakness is...\na beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This may be dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:05.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Worried, Sango decides to\nfollow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:09.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But deep in that mountain\nwas a sad legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:14.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Temptress in the Mist"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
